title: Joseph Arthur - 2014-06-04 - Sonic Boom Records
description:
JOSEPH ARTHUR
June 4, 2014
Seattle, WA, USA
Sonic Boom Records

I'd heard of Joseph Arthur because he's the singer for RNDM, a band that Pearl Jam's Jeff Ament is also in. I recalled liking what I'd heard from them, so I went to this. And it was good. I didn't realize he'd only be playing Lou Reed songs, but that's fine with me. 

Sound's good. Samples below.
